---
import BaseTW from "../../layouts/BaseTW.astro";
import ShapeFooter from "../../components/ShapeFooter.astro";
---

<BaseTW
  title="尋找 NocoBase 合作伙伴 - 全球服務網絡為你的項目保駕護航"
  description="NocoBase 擁有遍佈全球的合作伙伴網絡，提供專業的系統開發、系統集成與技術運維支持服務。提交你的需求，我們為你匹配最合適的服務夥伴。"
  keywords="NocoBase 合作伙伴, 尋找夥伴, 系統開發, 系統集成, 技術運維, 服務實施"
>
  <!-- Hero/Banner Start -->
  <section class="bg-half-170 bg-light d-table w-100">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-10 text-center">
          <div class="title-heading">
            <span class="badge bg-soft-primary mb-3">尋找合作伙伴</span>
            <h1 class="fw-bold mt-2 mb-3">找到合適的 NocoBase 夥伴，助你成功</h1>
            <p class="para-desc mx-auto text-muted">NocoBase 擁有遍佈全球的合作伙伴網絡，提供基於 NocoBase 的系統開發、系統集成、部署運維等服務，為你的項目保駕護航。</p>
            <div class="mt-4 pt-2">
              <a href="#submit-requirements" class="btn btn-primary me-3">
                <i class="uil uil-file-edit-alt me-1"></i>提交需求
              </a>
              <a href="#partner-fit" class="btn btn-outline-primary">
                <i class="uil uil-arrow-down me-1"></i>瞭解詳情
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div><!--end col-->
      </div><!--end row-->
    </div><!--end container-->
  </section><!--end section-->
  <!-- Hero/Banner End -->

  <!-- Partner Fit Start -->
  <section class="section" id="partner-fit">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-12">
          <div class="section-title text-center mb-4 pb-2">
            <h4 class="title mb-3">哪些情況適合找合作伙伴</h4>
            <p class="para-desc mx-auto text-muted mb-0">如果你正面臨以下情況，NocoBase 合作伙伴可以幫助你更高效地推進項目落地。</p>
          </div>
        </div><!--end col-->
      </div><!--end row-->

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mt-4 pt-2">
          <div class="card border-0 features feature-primary feature-clean course-feature p-4 overflow-hidden shadow h-100">
            <div class="icons text-start">
              <i class="uil uil-users-alt rounded h3 mb-0"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body p-0 mt-4 d-flex flex-column">
              <h5 class="title text-dark mb-2">沒有足夠的內部開發團隊</h5>
              <p class="text-muted">缺少熟悉企業應用搭建、交付與維護的團隊時，可以藉助夥伴快速補齊實施能力。</p>
              <i class="uil uil-users-alt full-img"></i>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div><!--end col-->

        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mt-4 pt-2">
          <div class="card border-0 features feature-primary feature-clean course-feature p-4 overflow-hidden shadow h-100">
            <div class="icons text-start">
              <i class="uil uil-rocket rounded h3 mb-0"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body p-0 mt-4 d-flex flex-column">
              <h5 class="title text-dark mb-2">需要快速上線業務系統</h5>
              <p class="text-muted">當項目時間緊、需要儘快驗證業務流程或交付系統時，夥伴服務能顯著縮短建設週期。</p>
              <i class="uil uil-rocket full-img"></i>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div><!--end col-->

        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mt-4 pt-2">
          <div class="card border-0 features feature-primary feature-clean course-feature p-4 overflow-hidden shadow h-100">
            <div class="icons text-start">
              <i class="uil uil-setting rounded h3 mb-0"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body p-0 mt-4 d-flex flex-column">
              <h5 class="title text-dark mb-2">需要定製開發、培訓或運維服務</h5>
              <p class="text-muted">如果你不僅需要軟件，還需要長期陪跑與支持，選擇夥伴服務更加穩妥。</p>
              <i class="uil uil-setting full-img"></i>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div><!--end col-->
      </div><!--end row-->
    </div><!--end container-->
  </section><!--end section-->
  <!-- Partner Fit End -->

  <!-- Services Start -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-12">
          <div class="section-title text-center mb-4 pb-2">
            <h4 class="title mb-4">NocoBase 夥伴能為你做什麼</h4>
            <p class="para-desc mx-auto text-muted mb-0">無論是全新開發還是現有系統升級，NocoBase 合作伙伴為你提供端到端的專業服務。</p>
          </div>
        </div><!--end col-->
      </div><!--end row-->

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mt-4 pt-2">
          <div class="card border-0 features feature-primary feature-clean course-feature p-4 overflow-hidden shadow h-100">
            <div class="icons text-start">
              <i class="uil uil-laptop-cloud rounded h3 mb-0"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body p-0 mt-4">
              <h5 class="title text-dark">系統開發</h5>
              <p class="text-muted mt-2">基於 NocoBase 平臺進行定製化應用開發，滿足你獨特的業務需求。從需求分析、方案設計到開發交付，全流程專業服務。</p>
              <i class="uil uil-laptop-cloud full-img"></i>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div><!--end col-->

        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mt-4 pt-2">
          <div class="card border-0 features feature-primary feature-clean course-feature p-4 overflow-hidden shadow h-100">
            <div class="icons text-start">
              <i class="uil uil-link-alt rounded h3 mb-0"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body p-0 mt-4">
              <h5 class="title text-dark">系統集成</h5>
              <p class="text-muted mt-2">將 NocoBase 與你現有的 ERP、CRM、OA 等系統無縫對接，打通數據孤島，實現業務流程的自動化與統一管理。</p>
              <i class="uil uil-link-alt full-img"></i>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div><!--end col-->

        <div class="col-lg-4 col-md-6 mt-4 pt-2">
          <div class="card border-0 features feature-primary feature-clean course-feature p-4 overflow-hidden shadow h-100">
            <div class="icons text-start">
              <i class="uil uil-setting rounded h3 mb-0"></i>
            </div>
            <div class="card-body p-0 mt-4">
              <h5 class="title text-dark">技術運維支持</h5>
              <p class="text-muted mt-2">提供系統部署、升級維護、性能優化和故障排除等運維服務，確保你的 NocoBase 系統穩定高效運行。</p>
              <i class="uil uil-setting full-img"></i>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div><!--end col-->
      </div><!--end row-->
    </div><!--end container-->
  </section><!--end section-->
  <!-- Services End -->

  <!-- Submit Requirements Start -->
  <section class="section" id="submit-requirements">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-12 text-center">
          <h4 class="title mb-4">提交你的需求</h4>
          <p class="text-muted para-desc mx-auto mb-4">
            告訴我們你的項目需求，我們將匹配最合適的 NocoBase 夥伴，助力項目成功落地。
          </p>
        </div><!--end col-->
      </div><!--end row-->
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-8 col-md-10">
          <div class="card border-0 shadow rounded overflow-hidden">
            <iframe
              src="https://service-cn.nocobase.com/public-forms/qgont25zd77"
              style="width: 100%; min-height: 700px; border: none;"
              loading="lazy"
            ></iframe>
          </div>
        </div><!--end col-->
      </div><!--end row-->
    </div><!--end container-->
  </section><!--end section-->
  <!-- Submit Requirements End -->

  <ShapeFooter />
</BaseTW>
